name: 'LA'
description:
This set of nails all feature the colour blue in some way or another!  They have a square tip and each pair of nails are different from the next. They were made for a photoshoot so are therefore a one-off design.

The set has 10 different sizes, labelled 0 (the biggest) - 9 (the smallest).

Each set of nails comes in a little handmade box, complete with a nail file and tube of nail glue for ease of application.

Photos are of the item you will receive.

All items will be shipped using recorded delivery, within 2 working days. They are sent out in cute little boxes and bubble wrapped securely to ensure no breakages!
